But he won't say
who he is or where he's from.

106
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,920
Then send him away.

107
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,560
Yes, Boss.

108
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:23,520
Go check.

109
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,560
Yes, Boss.

110
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:40,160
