187
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:47,720
You say that like you once loved someone.

188
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:55,400
It's over.

189
00:22:56,760 --> 00:22:58,400
I don't need love anymore.

190
00:23:00,080 --> 00:23:03,080
