- Oh!

217
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,840
- Answer me.
- Okay.

218
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:04,480
Just watch the clip.

219
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:06,960
Here.

220
00:27:09,080 --> 00:27:10,600
Please just watch the clip.

221
00:27:34,280 --> 00:27:35,120
Yes?

222
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:38,400
