into treating me to a meal?

230
00:28:07,280 --> 00:28:10,440
I'll give you two meals. Dessert included.

231
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:11,880
No need for dessert.

232
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,720
You're sweet enough.

233
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:21,120
Well,

234
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:24,120
I'll bring Yong with me, okay?

235
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:26,240
