and he's not here.

267
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,880
He's never late.

268
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:36,240
He always arrives early.

269
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:38,640
Forget him. Your brother

270
00:31:39,280 --> 00:31:42,760
